RBAC - Role and RoleBinding same for clusterRole and ClusterRoleBinding
-----------------------------------------------------------------
1) Using Role & RoleBinding:
   We can restrict the resources for a specific namespace (ns) in the cluster.
   If we try to access resources in another namespace, it will throw an error.

2) Using ClusterRole & ClusterRoleBinding:
   We can restrict the resources for all the namespaces (ns) in a cluster.

